<h3 id="dashboard-iÃ§in-admin-kullanÄ±cÄ±-oluÅŸturma">Dashboard iÃ§in admin kullanÄ±cÄ± oluÅŸturma</h3>

<p><a href="https://github.com/kubernetes/dashboard/blob/master/docs/user/access-control/creating-sample-user.md">Buradaki kurulum</a> ile tam yetkili kullanÄ±cÄ± oluÅŸturulur.</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
